02:29.004 --> 02:32.028
OH, MY, THAT WAS QUITE
THE PREDICAMENT.

02:33.000 --> 02:36.014
FIRST THERE'S A GIANT MONSTER
EATING THE CITY,

02:36.016 --> 02:38.012
THEN I'M PUT ON HOLD FOREVER,

02:38.014 --> 02:40.024
AND NOW MY HAT IS GONE!

02:40.026 --> 02:42.014
Blossom: OH, MAYOR?

02:42.016 --> 02:43.028
YES?

02:47.009 --> 02:49.026
MY HAT!

02:51.002 --> 02:54.016
WHOO-HOO! LOOK AT ME, HUH?

02:54.018 --> 02:57.020
THANKS TO YOU GIRLS,
TOWNSVILLE IS SAFE,

02:57.022 --> 03:00.026
AND MY HAT IS BACK
IN ITS PROPER PLACE.

03:00.028 --> 03:04.022
HOW CAN I EVER REPAY YOU
FOR SAVING THE DAY?

03:04.024 --> 03:06.012
NO PAYMENT
NECESSARY, MAYOR.

03:06.014 --> 03:08.001
WE WERE JUST
DOING OUR JOB.

03:08.003 --> 03:09.012
