YOU LIKE IT, GIRLS.
IT'S FROM AN--

03:49.022 --> 03:53.001
MMM...

03:53.003 --> 03:55.004
AHH...

03:55.006 --> 03:57.024
OHH...

03:57.026 --> 03:59.020
GIRLS?

04:00.016 --> 04:03.003
