04:17.018 --> 04:20.013
UH, GIRLS?

04:26.025 --> 04:30.016
THAT WAS AMAZING.

04:30.018 --> 04:32.002
YEAH.
YEAH.

04:32.004 --> 04:33.005
YES. AHEM.

04:33.007 --> 04:36.015
