THAT SOUNDS FAIR.
ONE PIECE PER--

04:52.002 --> 04:53.011
Girls: BYE, MAYOR!

04:53.013 --> 04:56.010
OH, OK. GOOD-BYE!

05:50.019 --> 05:52.023
