06:06.019 --> 06:09.005
BLAH BLAH BLAH BLAH...
SAVE THE DAY!

06:09.007 --> 06:11.016
IN ORDER FOR SOMETHING
TO BE SAVED,

06:11.018 --> 06:16.008
