TO COMMIT A CRIME.

06:26.016 --> 06:28.011
Blossom:
THANK YOU FOR COMING.

06:28.013 --> 06:30.022
WE ARE IN NEED OF
YOUR SERVICES.

06:30.024 --> 06:32.016
JUST DO WHAT
YOU DO BEST...

06:32.018 --> 06:34.010
