09:37.004 --> 09:39.023
[CROWD CHEERING]

09:42.012 --> 09:44.012
WOW!
WOW!
WOW!

09:48.014 --> 09:49.010
AHEM.

09:49.012 --> 09:51.012
THANK YOU
FOR THIS HONOR, MAYOR.

09:51.014 --> 09:53.005
I PROMISE ALL OF YOU,

09:53.007 --> 09:54.015
AS LONG AS WE'RE HERE,

09:54.017 --> 09:59.017
EVIL AND WRONGDOERS
WILL NOT PREVAIL IN
TOWNSVILLE!

09:59.019 --> 10:03.006
